      "writtenOn": "2020-06-22T21:02:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "++++1. sinkpb removed.\n\nI updated upload functions to take io.ReadSeeker, instead of io.Reader. The stream cursors need to be reset to 0 after the hash calculated.",
      "parentUuid": "ce3e861d_56e8f3b2",
